dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents parks for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in YE2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Milwaukee_Parks_YE2016.[This data set consists of the property boundaries of all the Milwaukee County park sites.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[The data set is intended to delineate lands that are under the jurisdiction of the Milwaukee County Parks Department.]
